import com.eviware.soapui.support.XmlHolder import com.eviware.soapui.impl.wsdl.testcase.WsdlTestRunContext import groovy.util.XmlSlurper
log.info"Addition"
valA=(Math.random()*1000).toInteger() valB=(Math.random()*1000).toInteger()
log.info("First Number: " + valA) log.info("Second Number: " + valB)
//log.info valA /*
valA=testRunner.testCase.testSuite.getPropertyValue("intA") A=valA.toInteger() valB=testRunner.testCase.testSuite.getPropertyValue("intB") B=valB.toInteger()
*/ def req= testRunner.testCase.testSuite.testCases["TestCase 1"].testSteps["Add"].getPropertyValue("Request")
def newReq=new XmlHolder(req) newReq.setNodeValue("//tem:Add/tem:intA",valA) newReq.setNodeValue("//tem:Add/tem:intB",valB) def newXml=newReq.getXml();
testRunner.testCase.testSuite.testCases["TestCase 1"].testSteps["Add"].setPropertyValue("Request",newXml)
def addTestStep=testRunner.testCase.testSuite.testCases["TestCase 1"].testSteps["Add"] def context=new WsdlTestRunContext(addTestStep)
addTestStep.run(testRunner,context)
def res=testRunner.testCase.testSuite.testCases["TestCase 1"].testSteps["Add"].getPropertyValue("Response") def slurper=new XmlSlurper()
parsedResponse=slurper.parseText(res) log.info(parsedResponse)
log.info result=valA+valB
assert result==parsedResponse.toInteger()
